ly only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/slot\"><code>&lt;slot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/source\"><code>&lt;source&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"nonStdElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/spacer\"><code>&lt;spacer&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"übersicht","title":"Übersicht","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das <em>HTML Underline Element</em> (<code>&lt;u&gt;</code>) versieht Text mit einem Unterstrich, also einer Linie unter der Basislinie des Textinhalts.</p>\n\n<p>In HTML5, repräsentiert dieses Element ein Textfeld mit einem unausgesprochenen, also nur gerenderten, nicht-textuellen Vermerk, so wie die Beschreibung eines Textes, als sei es eine Eigenschaft eines chinesisches&nbsp;Textes (eine chinesische Textmarkierung), oder als ob der Text falsch buchstabiert sei.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\"><strong>Gebrauchsnotiz: </strong>So wie alle stylisierenden Elemente, wird <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a> in HTML 4 und XHTML 1 nicht mehr unterstützt. Das Attribut wurde aber wieder in HTML5 zusammen mit anderen Wortbedeutungen aufgenommen. Wenn ein Text unterstrichen werden soll in einer nicht-begriffsbestimmenden Art und Weise, sollte ein <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Element eingesetzt werden, oder andere angepasste Elemente, und es mit <a href=\"/en-US/CSS\" title=\"en/CSS\">CSS</a> formatieren <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/text-decoration\"><code>text-decoration</code></a>, also mit der <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">underline</span> Eigenschaft.</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribute","title":"Attribute","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">Dieses Element enthält nur das </span><a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">globale Attribut</a><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">.</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"tips_und_bemerkungen","title":"Tips und Bemerkungen","isH3":false,"content":"<p style=\"line-height: 21px;\"><b>Tip:</b> Das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a> Element nicht benutzen wo es mit einem Hyperlink verwechselt werden kann.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\"><strong>Notiz:</strong> Die HTML 5 Spezifikation errinnert Entwickler dass andere Elemente passender sind als <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a>.</span></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dom_interface","title":"DOM Interface","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Element implementiert das <code><a href=\"/en-US/DOM/element\" title=\"en/DOM/element\">HTMLElement</a></code> Interface.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\"><strong>Implementation-Notiz: </strong>bis zur Version Gecko 1.9.2 inklusive, implementiert Firefox das <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Interface für dieses Element.</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>u</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Today's Special<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>u</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>: Salmon<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">text-decoration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>underline<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Today's Special<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>: Salmon\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><u>Today's Special</u>: Salmon</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Today's Special</span>: Salmon</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>u</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>All<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>u</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> of that is explained in <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>u</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Dive into Python<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>u</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>.\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><u>All</u> of that is explained in <u>Dive into Python</u>.</p>\n\n<p>Sollte ersetzt werden durch</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>All<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> of that is explained in <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>cite</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Dive into Python<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>cite</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>.\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><em>All</em> of that is explained in <cite>Dive into Python</cite>.</p>\n\n<p>CSS sollte benutzt werden um diese Elemente zu formatieren.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Die <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/i\"><code>&lt;i&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/em\"><code>&lt;em&gt;</code></a>, and <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/cite\"><code>&lt;cite&gt;</code></a> Elemente sollten, vom Fall abhängend, anstatt benutzt werden.</li>\n <li>Die CSS&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/text-decoration\"><code>text-decoration</code></a> Eigenschaft sollte benutzt werden für dasselbe Aussehen als das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a> Element.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p>\n\n<div id=\"sect4\"></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Übersicht","id":"übersicht"},{"text":"Attribute","id":"attribute"},{"text":"Tips und Bemerkungen","id":"tips_und_bemerkungen"},{"text":"DOM Interface","id":"dom_interface"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Das HTML Underline Element (<u>) versieht Text mit einem Unterstrich, also einer Linie unter der Basislinie des Textinhalts.","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<u>: The Unarticulated Annotation (Underline) element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"u","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<u> : l'élément d'annotation non textuelle","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<u>: 非言語的注釈 (下線) 要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<u>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<u>: Элемент слабой аннотации (подчёркивание)","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<u>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/html/element/u","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/html/element/u/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: HyperText Markup Language"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u","title":"<u>"}],"pageTitle":"<u> - HTML: HyperText Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}